SUMMARY:How to Read a Poem
DESCRIPTION:How to Read a Poem: \nJoin us on Wednesday\, March 25 from 7-9 p.m. in the Hugo House Theater Lobby for a reading from ten local poets: Brian Giddens\, Diane Qi\, Jay French\, Laura Titzer\, Margaret O’Donnell\, Mariko Navin\, Mark Onnen\, Meg Hofer\, Mike Nadal\, and Wendy Roach. Hosted by Jeanine Walker. Free to attend. 
URL:https://hugohouse.org/event/how-to-read-a-poem-5_2026-03-25/
END:VEVENT
